COGNIZANT README

Build

If not already installed, install Node, on a Mac:

brew i node

If not already installed globally, install gulp and bower:

npm i gulp bower -g

Install Bower Front-End Components:

bower i

Install Node Build Components:

npm i

$$$:

gulp
